        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for essay [<hi rend="italic">Cras credemus: a treatise on the cultivation of the potato from the seed, having for proposed results the extinction of the disease</hi> (1876)] and seeds. Thinks principle on which JT is acting is right.</p>  
<p>Cannot allow publication of his earlier letter [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">10368</hi>], as he cannot recall what he wrote.</p> 
        </abstract>
